parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of Takata airbag recall parts may lead to a delay in repairing the defective airbags, which can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: None
as the issue is related to the unavailability of parts for a recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cylinder head can cause the engine to stall, leading to a loss of power and control, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The check engine warning light illuminates
the engine stalls or runs rough
the vehicle overheats
the exhaust valves are worn or cracked
the valves recede into the head
and the engine has low compression.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to adjust the valves properly can cause the engine to stall, leading to a loss of power and control, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The check engine warning light illuminates
the engine stalls or runs rough
the valves are out of adjustment
and the engine has low compression.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the radiator can cause the engine to overheat, leading to a loss of power and control, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle overheats
and the radiator has numerous pinholes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch hydraulic system can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
and the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Cruise Control and Engine Revving Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cruise control system can cause the engine to rev up unexpectedly, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The cruise control light comes on
the engine revs up

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to hesitate or refuse to shift gears, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: Hesitation to shift gears

symptoms: Clunking noise while shifting manual transmission

loud noises while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature tire wear can cause loss of traction, leading to potential accidents and loss of control.

premature tire replacement.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rear glass trunk lid leaks can cause water damage and safety issues.
